reviewText: My nieces and nephews loved it.

This is probably a good value for people with kids but too many of the movies will be enjoyed by kids only. There are some really good, decent movies out there for adults to enjoy, unfortunately there is only one or maybe two in this collection. Had the movie collection been titled "Beloved Children's Favorites - 20 Movie Collection" it would be what it claimed to be - children's favorites.
Item arrived quickly and as expected. Satisfied with the quality.
